(1, 35, 'About Us', 'about-us', '', '<center>\r\n	<h2 style="text-align: center; margin:50px 0 0 0;">\r\n		<span style="font-size:70px;"><em><span style="font-family:aubreyregular;">Profile</span></em></span></h2>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Amici Events and Catering is a boutique caterer in Singapore offering tantalizing food at your desired venue. Helmed by a team of culinary experts, menus are crafted in-house to reflect the elegance and diversity of Eastern and Western cuisines. The finesse of the gourmet dishes selected for your guests will be enhanced with our exquisite style in presentation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		On top of the popular buffet spreads, Amici provides fine dining courses, an extensive variety of delectable canapés, personal chefs for hire, uniformed butlers at your call, live stations for corporate functions, weddings and home parties.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Experience a seamlessly tailored service to suit your event and create unforgettable memories with Amici Events and Catering, Singapore''s best kept secret.</p>\r\n	<h2 style="text-align: center; margin:50px 0 0 0;">\r\n		<span style="font-size:70px;"><em><span style="font-family:aubreyregular;">History</span></em></span></h2>\r\n	<p>\r\n		The Amici Group was founded in 2000 by Willie, an aficionado of good food and service. Stemming from a multi-awards winning semi-fine dining restaurant in Holland Village and with its catering arm in Joo Chiat, the Amici Group has since grown from strength to strength to become a renowned brand in the Food and Beverage industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		In 2012, Willie was conferred the Spirit of Enterprise Award for his outstanding efforts in growing the business. Today, the Amici Group runs from a state-of-the-art factory sized kitchen that is ever ready to serve guests consistently throughout the island and penetrate into the region to share her gourmet pleasures.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</center>\r\n', '', 1, 0, 0, 2, '2014-07-29 02:19:09', 522, '', '2014-08-06 10:25:38', 522, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-07-29 02:19:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 9, 0, 4, '', '', 1, 2516, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
